Name: mine

Description: A place where you can mine metal scraps.

Interface:
    ----------------------
           THE MINE
       get metal scraps

     Metal scraps: <metal>

Choices:

    Name: mine
    Description: Mines 1 metal scrap.
    Function: Give you 1 metal scrap and decreases your pickaxe's durability by 1.
    Usage: Mine
    Requirements: You must have a pickaxe.

    Name: back
    Description: Moves you back to the menu.
    Function: Moves you back to the menu.
    Usage: back
    Requirements: None


Entering:
    None

Leaving:
    None

Extra Info:
    None
